<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Security-Policy" content="default-src 'none'; style-src <%= cspSource %>; img-src <%= cspSource %>; script-src <%= cspSource %>">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= cssUri %>">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= baseUri %>/templates/welcome.css">
  <title>Welcome to OpenShift Connector</title>
</head>

<body>

<div class="welcome-sections">
  <div class="section-div">
    <div class="title-wrapper">
      <img src="<%= baseUri %>/icons/extension.png" class="extension-icon">
      <h2 class="title-header">OpenShift Connector Extension</h2>
      <% if (status) { %>
        <span class="preview"><%= status %></span>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <p>Welcome! This extension provides tools to get you up and running with OpenShift or Kubernetes
    application development in <%= appName %>.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section-row">
    <img src="<%= baseUri %>/icons/create.png" class="section-icon" >
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-name">Create New Component</div>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.component.createFromLocal">Create a New OpenShift Component</a></li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-row">
    <img src="<%= baseUri %>/icons/cluster.png" class="section-icon" >
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-name">Create or Use Existing Cluster</div>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.explorer.addCluster">Add a New OpenShift Cluster</a></li>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.explorer.login">Login in to a Cluster</a></li>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.explorer.switchContext">Select Kubernetes Context</a></li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-row">
    <img src="<%= baseUri %>/icons/run.png" class="section-icon" >
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-name">Run/Debug Locally or in Cluster</div>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Run and debug your component locally using VSCode Extensions</li>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.component.createFromLocal">Create New Component</a> from your source code and <a href="command:openshift.component.push">push</a> it to cluster</li>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.component.debug">Debug</a> component running in cluster</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-row">
    <img src="<%= baseUri %>/icons/feedback.png" class="section-icon" >
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-name">Tell Us What You Think</div>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="command:openshift.explorer.reportIssue">Create an issue</a> in extension's github.com repository</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-row">
    <img src="<%= baseUri %>/icons/links.png" class="section-icon" >
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-name">Additional Information</div>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://code-ready.github.io/crc/">Red Hat CodeReady Containers</a> - run single node local OpenShift 4.x cluster</li>
          <li><a href="http://bit.ly/3rSvzOx">minishift</a>/<a href="http://red.ht/3opF1XC">CDK</a> - run single node local OpenShift 3.x cluster</li>
          <li><a href="http://red.ht/3rUUzoe">Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform</a> - build, deploy and manage your applications across cloud- and on-premise infrastructure</li>
          <li><a href="http://red.ht/3bdr7E8">Red Hat OpenShift Dedicated</a> - single-tenant, high-availability Kubernetes clusters in the public cloud</li>
          <li><a href="http://red.ht/3oeVPjM">Microsoft Azure Red Hat OpenShift</a> - fully managed Red Hat OpenShift service on Microsoft Azure</li>
          <li><a href="http://red.ht/3bbSVso">Red Hat OpenShift Online</a> - the fastest way for developers to build, host and scale applications in the public cloud</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-div">
    <input type="checkbox" id="showWhenUsingExtension" <% if (checkboxValue) { %> checked <% } %>>
    <label for="showWhenUsingExtension">Show welcome page when OpenShift Connector Extension is activated</label>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
<script src="<%= jsUri %>"></script>
</html>
